          </div>
          <div class="rv-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rv-text">Muy eficientes en su labor y servicio publicitario.</p>
          <div class="rv-verified"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1A73E8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/></svg> Verificado por Google</div>
        </div>

        <div class="rv-card rv-featured">
          <div class="rv-top">
            <div class="rv-avatar" style="background:#1565C0;">C</div>
            <div class="rv-info">
              <p class="rv-name">Christian Pajuelo</p>
              <p class="rv-date">13 jun 2025</p>
            </div>
            <svg class="rv-g" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" aria-label="Google"><path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"/><path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/><path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z"/><path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="rv-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rv-text">El equipo siempre está disponible y muestra una gran disposición para ayudarnos a optimizar nuestras campañas. Su acompañamiento constante y su capacidad para brindarnos soluciones efectivas han sido clave para mejorar nuestros resultados. Valoramos mucho su compromiso y profesionalismo.</p>
          <div class="rv-verified"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1A73E8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/></svg> Verificado por Google</div>
        </div>

        <div class="rv-card">
          <div class="rv-top">
            <div class="rv-avatar" style="background:#6A1B9A;">A</div>
            <div class="rv-info">
              <p class="rv-name">Alfonso Llamo</p>
              <p class="rv-date">13 jun 2025</p>
            </div>
            <svg class="rv-g" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" aria-label="Google"><path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"/><path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/><path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z"/><path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="rv-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rv-text">Muy buena labor en el servicio de publicidad. Resultados rápidos y equipo muy profesional.</p>
          <div class="rv-verified"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1A73E8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/></svg> Verificado por Google</div>
        </div>

        <div class="rv-card">
          <div class="rv-top">
            <div class="rv-avatar" style="background:#B71C1C;">M</div>
            <div class="rv-info">
              <p class="rv-name">Manuel Sáez</p>
              <p class="rv-date">13 jun 2025</p>
            </div>
            <svg class="rv-g" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" aria-label="Google"><path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"/><path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/><path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z"/><path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="rv-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rv-text">Rápida atención y muy eficientes. Recomendados para publicidad por correo masivo en Perú.</p>
          <div class="rv-verified"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1A73E8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/></svg> Verificado por Google</div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <button class="rv-arrow rv-next" id="rvNext" aria-label="Siguiente">›</button>
    </div>

    <div class="rv-dots" id="rvDots">
      <span class="rv-dot active"></span>
      <span class="rv-dot"></span>
      <span class="rv-dot"></span>
      <span class="rv-dot"></span>
    </div>

    <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=BanaMailing+Peru+reviews" target="_blank" class="reviews-cta">
      Ver todas las reseñas en Google →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-section {
    background: #F8F7FF;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 5rem 4rem;
  }
  .reviews-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .reviews-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .reviews-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #3c4043;
    padding: 5px 16px; border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .reviews-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .reviews-title em { color: var(--purple); font-style: normal; }
  .reviews-score {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px; padding: 8px 20px;
  }
  .rs-num { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .rs-stars { font-size: 18px; color: #FBBC05; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .rs-count { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; }

  .reviews-track-wrap {
    position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .reviews-track {
    display: flex; gap: 18px;
    overflow-x: auto; scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none; padding: 8px 12px 16px;
    scroll-padding-left: 12px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .reviews-track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .rv-arrow {
    width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #fff;
    font-size: 22px; color: var(--text); cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1;
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .rv-arrow:hover { background: var(--purple); color: #fff; border-color: var(--purple); transform: scale(1.05); }

  .rv-card {
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.5rem;
    min-width: 300px; max-width: 340px;
    scroll-snap-align: start; flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .rv-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(103,76,196,0.12); }
  .rv-card.rv-featured { border: 2px solid #DDD6FE; }

  .rv-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .rv-avatar {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
    color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .rv-info { flex: 1; }
  .rv-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 1px; }
  .rv-date { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--muted); }
  .rv-g { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .rv-stars { font-size: 17px; color: #FBBC05; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .rv-text { font-size: 13.5px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; flex: 1; }
  .rv-verified {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
    font-size: 11px; color: #1A73E8; font-weight: 600;
  }

  .rv-dots {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .rv-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #D1D5DB; cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .rv-dot.active { background: var(--purple); transform: scale(1.3); }

  .reviews-cta {
    display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--purple);
    text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .reviews-cta:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .reviews-section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .rv-card { min-width: 270px; }
    .rv-arrow { display: none; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  let rvIndex = 0;
  const track = document.getElementById('reviewsTrack');
  const dotEls = document.querySelectorAll('.rv-dot');
  const cardEls = document.querySelectorAll('.rv-card');

  function goToReview(i: number) {
    if (!track || !cardEls[i]) return;
    rvIndex = i;
    const trackEl = track as HTMLElement;
    const cardEl = cardEls[i] as HTMLElement;
    const scrollLeft = trackEl.scrollLeft + cardEl.getBoundingClientRect().left - trackEl.getBoundingClientRect().left;
    trackEl.scrollTo({ left: scrollLeft, behavior: 'smooth' });
    dotEls.forEach((d, j) => d.classList.toggle('active', j === i));
  }

  document.getElementById('rvPrev')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    goToReview(Math.max(0, rvIndex - 1));
  });
  document.getElementById('rvNext')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    goToReview(Math.min(cardEls.length - 1, rvIndex + 1));
  });
  dotEls.forEach((d, i) => d.addEventListener('click', () => goToReview(i)));

  setInterval(() => {
    rvIndex = (rvIndex + 1) % cardEls.length;
    goToReview(rvIndex);
  }, 5000);
</script>
